high_descs: Turn left, turn left again to get to the refrigerator.
Take the butterknife on the shelf.
Shut the door, do a quarter turn and turn back to the refrigerator.
Open the door, put the butter knife in the bowl.
Take the butter knife and the bowl on the shelf.
Turn 270 degrees counter-clockwise and go to the counter. .
Put the butter knife and the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Take a butter knife and bowl out of the fridge to put them on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, look into the fridge.
Open the fridge, take the butter knife from the fridge, close the fridge.
Look around the countertop and fridge.
Open the fridge, put the butter knife inside the bowl on the fridge.
Take the bowl from the fridge, close the fridge.
Turn around, look into the kitchen countertop.
Put the bowl along with butter knife on the countertop behind the box.
anns.task_desc: To get the bowl and butter knife from the fridge, put in on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and look to the fridge right in front of you.
Pick up the butter knife that's in the fridge.
Look to the fridge again.
Place the knife inside the bowl that's in the fridge.
Pick up the bowl with the knife in it.
Look to the counters to the right of the fridge.
Place the bowl on the corner of the counters, next to the cardboard box.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a butter knife in it on a counter.
